<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>SkillSwap</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gradient-to-tr from-indigo-50 via-purple-100 to-pink-50 min-h-screen">

    <section class="px-10 py-20 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-indigo-700 mb-6 leading-tight drop-shadow-md">
          Exchange Skills, <br />Build Your Future 🚀
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Welcome to <strong>SkillSwap</strong> — the coolest place to teach what you know and learn what you love.
          Build connections, explore talents, and unlock endless possibilities.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="/register" class="bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow-md transition">
            Join Now
          </a>
          <a href="/login" class="bg-white text-indigo-600 border border-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-50 transition">
            Already a Member?
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden md:block">
        <img src="/images/hero.png" alt="Illustration" class="max-w-md drop-shadow-xl" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-10 bg-white">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-indigo-700">Why SkillSwap?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-800 mb-4">No Money Needed 💰</h3>
          <p>Exchange your skill with someone else's. It's free, fair, and fun!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-800 mb-4">Build Real Connections 🤝</h3>
          <p>Find like-minded people to grow together — it’s a community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-800 mb-4">Teach & Learn 📚</h3>
          <p>Become both a student and a mentor. Everyone has something to share.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="text-center py-6 text-gray-500 text-sm">
      Made by Anjali✌️ | © 2026 SkillSwap
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
